---

<Layout
  title="Startups & Scaleups"
  description="How Green Orbit Digital supports early-stage innovators in the space, tech, and climate sectors with sustainable, strategic marketing."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="py-12 space-y-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <HeroSection
      title="Startups & Scaleups"
      description="Supporting early-stage innovators with sustainable, strategic marketing that accelerates growth and builds long-term impact."
    />

    <section class="space-y-6 text-white">
      <p>
        Startups and scaleups in the space, tech, and climate innovation sectors face a unique challenge: 
        gaining visibility, establishing credibility, and communicating complex capabilities in competitive markets. 
        Green Orbit Digital partners with founding teams to articulate their value, sharpen messaging, and build 
        trust with investors, customers, and collaborators.
      </p>

      <p>
        Whether developing satellite-enabled services, climate-tech platforms, or advanced engineering solutions, 
        we translate deep technology into clear, compelling narratives that resonate with the people you need to reach.
        Our sustainable-first approach ensures responsible growth, helping you scale with purpose, clarity, and confidence.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
    <!-- CTA -->
